{"title":"千里海洋变渔港","authors":["黄辉"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里海洋变渔港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（咸水歌）　黄辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天连水来水连天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天星斗数不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海里宝藏无穷尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更比星斗多万千。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佛山专区海岸长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超过七百公里长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小渔港廿五个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边大海是渔场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日照海面闪金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的号召切勿忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里海洋变渔港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部荒滩变?塘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多力大人人知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器开船好捕鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四年实现机械化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取机械化不能迟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年海产不简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百六十三万担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四年要增五六倍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千万担要实行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能装雷达电报机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥联络得及时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小渔港现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大船机轮去捕鱼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航标灯塔来安装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上建设避风塘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海洋气候能预告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉鱼人仔免徬徨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建房造屋要有砖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装机修船要用钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩大积累加勤俭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发动投资装新船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦战三年有根基，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海港变成风景区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边建设疗养院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子孙万代享欢娱。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}